   d. change cateogoryRepository class to interface

    public interface WritoRepository extends JpaRepository<Writo,String>

    Spring does this internally:

        Detects interface
        Creates a runtime class (proxy)
        Implements all methods using Hibernate
        Uses DB (H2/MySQL) to execute SQL

    👉 So YOU never write implementation . All implementation is done by spring internally
   e. whatever ouptut we will get through writoRepository will be optional
   f. It Require NoArgsconstructor in model class as to create object automatically

